<div class="content">
  <p>Five groups of viewers had different invitations flows depending on which events they were invited to, their party size, and their dietary restrictions. Submission saved a cookie with their form object so that the site would reflect their immediate suggestions, and then the site would rebuild, reflecting those choices as pulled from Netlify Forms. They were then able to return and edit their selection, seeing their past choices.</p>
